name: SATStudy
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: s. a. t. study
des:
This skill will read a word, and then read its meaning. The word is chosen at random from thousands of words. Every time you use this skill, you are unlikely to encounter the same words. You can use this skill to study for standardized tests. We recommend you use this skill everyday , for example before bedtime. You will slowly feel your vocabulary increase.

You can invoke this skill using "S.A.T. Study" (spelled out s a t), or "sat study" (rhymes with bat).
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
